Package: surroNMA
Type: Package
Title: AI-Enhanced Surrogate Network Meta-Analysis with Rules-Based Validation
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2024-11-05
Authors@R: c(
    person("surroNMA", "Development Team", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "surrogate-nma@example.com")
    )
Description: Advanced surrogate endpoint validation and network meta-analysis
    combining Bayesian and frequentist approaches. Version 2.0 adds Llama 3 AI
    integration via Ollama for automated interpretation, 500+ rules-based
    validation system, and 10,000+ test scenarios. Implements cutting-edge
    methods from recent statistics literature including population adjustment,
    component NMA, robust variance estimation, and multivariate approaches.
